downloadTitle: Microsoft Dynamics CRM Project Service Automation Demo Data
downloadDescription: Demo dataset for Microsoft Dynamics CRM Project Service Automation capabilities
detailsSection:
To become familiar with the project service automation capabilities in Microsoft Dynamics CRM, it’s useful to have a pre-configured environment to explore. For this purpose, we’ve created a separate managed solution that makes it easier to explore and learn about the new solution. Running this package deployer performs the following actions:
• Builds default parameters that drive behavior of project service
• Creates default working calendars
• Imports sample data such as resources, projects, prices, roles, and other key information
• Associates resources with the proper working calendar
• Updates images of contacts and accounts
systemRequirementsSection: Microsoft Dynamics CRM Online 2016 Update 1 and Project Service Automation capabilities solution
installInstructionSection:
Download the self-extracting file and extract the contents.  Read the Using the Demo Data Loader for 
Project Service Automation document
